3 September 2019 Joint media briefing on Gender Based Violence and Femicide The Minister in the Presidency for Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities, Maite Nkoana-Mashabane and the Minister of Justice and Correctional Services, Ronald Lamola will today brief media on the recent incidents of Gender-based Violence and Femicide. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date:  Tuesday, 03 September 2019  Time:  17H30  Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town. NB: There will be a video link to GCIS Ronnie Mamoepa Media Centre, 1035 Tshedimosetso House, Frances Baard Street, Hatfield Follow the conversation on @GovernmentZA @GCISMedia #GBV Enquiries:  Mmabatho Ramompi  Cell: 076 480 3513 Chrispin Phiri   Cell: 083 220 9691 Issued by Government Communication and Information System